message.entry: 函数 imfill 要求其第二个输入参数 LOCATIONS 具有 1 或 NDIMS(IM) 个列。

Function imfill does not support interactive location selection for empty images.
Function imfill does not support interactive location selection for code generation.
HOLES 必须为字符串或字符向量常量。
